ooter page number increments. The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog, repeatedly, to consume vertical space and force pagination.</fo:block><fo:block space-after="6pt" text-align="justify">Paragraph 29. This document spans several pages so the running header and footer repeat and the footer page number increments. The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog, repeatedly, to consume vertical space and force pagination.</fo:block><fo:block space-after="6pt" text-align="justify">Paragraph 30. This document spans several pages so the running header and footer repeat and the footer page number increments. The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog, repeatedly, to consume vertical space and force pagination.</fo:block>
      <fo:block id="endsection" break-before="page" font-size="16pt" font-weight="bold" color="#1a3c7b">The referenced section</fo:block>
      <fo:block space-before="6pt">This heading has id="endsection"; the cross-reference on the first page resolves to this page number.</fo:block>
    </fo:flow>
  </fo:page-sequence>
</fo:root>